      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "<b>Welcome to the VR Study!</b>\n\n<b>Overview:</b>\n\u2022 You will experience
    5 scenes.\n\u2022 After each scene, please finish a survey.\n\n<b>Exiting Scenes:</b>\n\u2022
    Each scene initially lasts for 60 seconds.\r\n\u2022 After 60 seconds, an Exit
    Pad will appear by the starting point. \r\n\u2022 Teleport to the Exit Pad to
    end the scene, or continue exploring.\n\n<b>Controls (Right Controller Only):</b>\n\u2022
    <b>Grip Button:</b> Press to teleport.\n\u2022 <b>Trigger Button:</b> Long press
    to get back to the starting point.\n\u2022 <b>Thumbstick:</b> Snap turn.\n\nWhen
    you're ready, teleport to the Exit Pad."
